<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>637</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>nǐ tīng cè ěr tīng 迦南637</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ tīng nǐ tīng, cè ěr tīng, lái zì yuǎn fāng de hū shēng.
 nǐ kàn nǐ kàn, fàng yǎn kàn, zhuāng jià dào chù yī piàn piàn.
 nǐ zǒu nǐ zǒu, xiàng qián zǒu, duō shǎo qī dài de yǎn shén.
 nǐ zuò nǐ zuò, nǐ qù zuò, zhǔ yǐ tuō fù zài nǐ shǒu.
 chàng zhe gē xiàng qián zǒu, shì rén jīng qí mó guǐ méng xiū.
 bèi zhe hé kǔn zhǔ jiā lì liàng, xiàn zài zhèng shì hǎo shí hòu.</lyrics>
</song>